Subject: [PATCH v5 6/6] drm/syncobj: Add a fast path to drm_syncobj_array_find
Date: Wed, 11 Jun 2025 15:00:57 +0100
Message-ID: <20250611140057.27259-7-tvrtko.ursulin@igalia.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.48.0
